text: Harold McGuirk (17 October 1906 - 19 June 1984) was an Australian cricketer. He played two first-class matches for New South Wales in 1926/27. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1906 births Category:1984 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers
